        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1 (3)</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2026 15:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in v1.1 (3)</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Fixed corner dragging</b> — Clicking now moves the selected corner instead of re-selecting the same one</li>
                    <li><b>Better corner switching</b> — Press Escape to deselect, click directly on a corner dot to switch</li>
                    <li><b>Improved cluster detection</b> — Works better when ML places corners close together</li>
                    <li><b>Auto-updates working</b> — Check for Updates in the app menu</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
