        <item>
            <title>Version 1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in v1.1</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>macOS 13+ support</b> — Now runs on Intel Macs with macOS Ventura and later</li>
                    <li><b>FFF/RAW fix</b> — Hasselblad 16-bit RAW files now display correctly on Intel Macs (no more mosaics or black images)</li>
                    <li><b>Reset button</b> — Clear bad ML detection and place corners manually</li>
                    <li><b>Click-to-relocate</b> — Select a corner, click anywhere to move it</li>
                    <li><b>Corner cycling</b> — Clustered corners cycle TL/TR/BR/BL on click</li>
                    <li><b>Auto-updates</b> — Future updates install with one click (Check for Updates in app menu)</li>
                    <li><b>Properly signed &amp; notarized</b> — No more Gatekeeper warnings</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
